(579,1,"2018-05-23 16:31:14","2018-05-23 16:31:14","<h2>The world of wine in the palm of your hand</h2>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-528\" src=\"http://catmain1.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/b-inspired-by-italian-style-700x449-300x192.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"192\" /></h3>\r\nThe Winewoo creators dreamed big: they wanted to create the largest existing wine labels database, covering 80% of the French wine market. That means over 200.000 varieties of wine! Their goal? Provide customers of quality French wine with an easy way to find out more information about the brands while on the go.\r\n<h3><strong>THE SOLUTION</strong></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCatchoom’s award-winning Image Recognition software is specifically designed to recognize cylindrical objects like bottles or cans, so it’s a perfect choice for apps in the Food &amp; Beverages industry.\r\n\r\nThanks to the massive scalability of our Enterprise Image Recognition solution, Winewoo was able to integrate more than 200,000 varieties in their database, without sacrificing the speed or accuracy.","","","trash","open","open","","__trashed-2","","","2018-05-23 16:31:14","2018-05-23 16:31:14","",0,"http://catmain1.local/?p=579",0,"post","",0),
