 currently co-sponsored by the Ministry of Industry, Energy and Tourism of Spain, in the National Plan of Scientific Investigation for three projects from July 2012 until December 2014, from August 2014 until December 2016, and from July 2015 until December 2017 (Project Numbers: TSI-020602-2012-25, TSI-100600-2014-13 and TSI-100600-2015-37).\" image=\"464\" text_color=\"#212122\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][icon_text box_type=\"normal\" icon_type=\"normal\" icon_position=\"top\" content_alignment=\"left\" icon_size=\"fa-4x\" use_custom_icon_size=\"yes\" custom_icon_size=\"90\" separator=\"no\" text=\"The EMPLEA initiative co-sponsors R&amp;D Projects developed by a technology company by investing in the acquisition of talented scientists. Catchoom participates in two projects co-sponsored by the Ministry of Economy and Competitiveness of Spain, in the National Plan of Scientific Investigation (Project Numbers: EMP-TU-2014-4017 and EMP-TU-2014-4018).\" image=\"465\" text_color=\"#212122\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" css=\".vc_custom_1527264735540{background-color: #f7f7f9 !important;}\" z_index=\"\"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"100px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]","About","","inherit","closed","closed","","45-autosave-v1","","","2018-05-25 16:14:05","2018-05-25 16:14:05","",45,"http://catmain1.local/45-autosave-v1/",0,"revision","",0);
